name: Henny ~The Ultimate Race
description: The Hennies are in it for the extinction, and it is a race they will win. No one will be able to call them chicken again, not by any known means of interstellar communication. **This artwork comes from a challenge I set myself - you can check the process here: https://ecency.com/creative/@penderis/what-doth-this-maketh-chickens-jets-and-the-city. To create something from 3 images only.
